name: Concealed
description:
Invigorated by the harmony of nature glorifying the goddess of the motherland, I recorded this elegiac voice to process the existing bewailings. Recorded at 12:52 AM 23 August 2021 in the heart of Borneo Island, I believed that a soul was responding to me, and I was replying to it.

Composed using a Sennheiser MKH416 microphone and preamps from Universal Audio Apollo Twin X and processed through Borderlands Granular app. I hope you dig this.
